1.Create Automation account.
2.Search Start/stop.
3.Create the Create a new workspace
4.Configure the parameters.
5.Select the start time 10:00AM and stop time 7:00AM.
6.We can enable email notification here.
7.Click on create.
8.Open Automation account.
9.Click on runbooks
10.Select the Schdulestartstop_parent.
11.Click on schedule and check the time zone's.
Now test this in test env:
1.Open automation account then click on runbook's
2.Click on Schdulestartstop_parent then select on Overview.
3.Then select the edit.
4.Click on text pane.
5.action start
6.vm name
7.click on start then observe the results.

Note: Make sure all are in same location and resource group.
